patthana19.3:1.1_0: Navipākaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca vipāko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana19.3:1.1_1: Navipākaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca vipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … pañca.
patthana19.3:2.1_0: Navipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca vipāko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana19.3:2.1_1: Navipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca nevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana19.3:3.1_1: Nanevavipākanavipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca vipāko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … pañca. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana19.3:4.1_1: adhipatiyā aṭṭhārasa …pe… aññamaññe soḷasa …pe… purejāte nava,
patthana19.3:4.1_2: āsevane cha …pe… vipāke pannarasa …pe… avigate dvāvīsa.
